oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: UNICEF tour - Australia - 1972 - part 5
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Part five of a 1972 UNICEF fundraiser tour performance in Australia. Featuring Tex Ritter (host) and Tom T. Hall (performer).
